---
import PrototypeLayout from "@/layouts/PrototypeLayout.astro";
---

<PrototypeLayout
	meta={{ title: "Taste Explorer" }}
	title="Taste Explorer"
	demoHeight="70vh"
	demoStyle="immersive"
>
	<div slot="demo" class="demo-wrapper">
		<video autoplay loop muted playsinline class="demo-video">
			<source src="/videos/taste-explorer-panning.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
		</video>
	</div>

	<!-- Content section -->
	<article class="prototype-content">
		<h2>About</h2>
		<p>
			An infinite random map of our collective taste. A collaborative tool where designers can
			upload images they find tasteful, creating a vast, ever-expanding visual landscape of
			aesthetic inspiration.
		</p>

		<h2>Technical Details</h2>
		<p>
			Built with PixiJS for high-performance 2D rendering, enabling smooth panning and zooming
			across an infinite canvas of curated imagery.
		</p>
		<ul>
			<li>
				<strong>Infinite canvas:</strong> Seamless exploration across an unbounded visual space
			</li>
			<li>
				<strong>S3 backend:</strong> Images stored and served via Amazon S3 for reliable,
				scalable delivery
			</li>
			<li>
				<strong>PixiJS rendering:</strong> GPU-accelerated graphics for buttery smooth 60fps
				interactions
			</li>
			<li>
				<strong>Random placement:</strong> Images scattered across the infinite plane, creating
				serendipitous discoveries
			</li>
		</ul>

		<h2>Concept</h2>
		<p>
			Taste Explorer is built on the idea that collective curation reveals patterns in aesthetic
			preference. By allowing designers to contribute images they find beautiful, interesting, or
			inspiring, the map becomes a living document of visual cultureâ€”a place to wander and
			discover unexpected connections between disparate sources of inspiration.
		</p>
	</article>
</PrototypeLayout>

<style>
	.demo-wrapper {
		position: relative;
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
		min-height: 70vh;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		overflow: hidden;
	}

	.demo-video {
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
		object-fit: cover;
	}

	.prototype-content {
		color: hsl(var(--theme-text));
	}

	.prototype-content h2 {
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		margin-top: 2rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.prototype-content h2:first-child {
		margin-top: 0;
	}

	.prototype-content p {
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		line-height: 1.75;
	}

	.prototype-content ul {
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		padding-left: 1.5rem;
		list-style-type: disc;
	}

	.prototype-content li {
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
		line-height: 1.75;
	}

	@media (max-width: 640px) {
		.demo-wrapper {
			min-height: 50vh;
		}
	}
</style>





